<p><b> II. Communications sent and replies received 
</b></p>
<p><b> A. Communications sent between 1 June and 30 November 2012 and replies received 
</b></p>
<p><b>by 31 January 2013 
</b></p>
<p>12. Communications are presented in chronological order. Copies of the full text of the communications sent and replies 
received may be accessed from the electronic version of this report available on the website of the Human Rights Council. Some 
names of individuals or other information have been rendered anonymous or otherwise unidentifiable. 
</p>
