<p><b>Torture;   
</b></p>
<p> 
Alleged beating and extraction of confession under torture. According to the 
information received, on 27 March 2012, Ms. X, a Uzbek national, was forced 
into a car by four men in plain clothes while in Jalal-Abad oblast market. She 
was taken to one of the offices of the Osh Oblast Department of Internal 
Affairs where she was subjected to beating by the employees with the purpose 
of obtaining a confession against her brother. After having spent four days in 
the Osh Oblast Department of Internal Affairs and the Kara-Suu Rayon 
Interior Unit, during which Ms. X was subjected to beating while being 
interrogated, she agreed to sign interrogation papers without being allowed to 
read them. She was told to bring in 200 USD after which she was released. 
Ms. X was threatened that if she complained about this incident, firearms or 
drugs would be planted in her house.  
