Jos&#233; da Silva Ver&#231;osa, members of the MXVPS, responsible for trespassing, 
harassing or disturbing purported property.  Following an alleged 
investigation of the activities of the Xingu +23 event, the civil police of the 
State of Par&#225; issued an arrest warrant of 11 persons, including Ms. Ant&#244;nia 
Melo, Mr. Ruy Marques, Father Alirio Bervian, Sisters Agnes and Flora 
