Ahmed Abdi, Mahad Salad Adan, Farhan James Abdulle, Hassan Osman 
Abdi and Ahmed Addow Anshur. Additionally, two journalists, Messrs. 
Abdulkadir Omar Abdulle and X, have been attacked, respectively, on 7 and 
12 July 2012. In all cases, the victims are believed to have been targeted in 
relation to their professional activities as journalists. 
