<p>Alleged risk of execution under charges which are not considered as most 
serious crimes. According to the information received, Mr. Gholamreza 
Khosravi Savadjani was scheduled to be executed on 10 September 2012, in 
the Islamic Repbulic of Iran under the charge of &#8213;enmity against God&#8214; 
</p>
