<p>Alleged detention and attacks against an atheist on allegations of &#8213;Defamation 
</p>
<p>of Religion&#8214;. According to the information received, on 13 September 2012, a 
</p>
<p>crowd gathered in front of Mr. Albert Saber Ayyad&#8216;s apartment with the 
</p>
<p>intention of attacking him over a video he had posted  on the internet that was 
viewed to be &#8213;defaming&#8214; Islam. Mr. Ayyad&#8216;s mother called the police for 
</p>
