training and which has been working on issues related to allegations of torture 
and ill-treatment in the country.  On 24 October 2012, the Khujand City Court 
of first instance granted the request made by the Ministry of Justice in July 
requesting the dissolution of the organization. Amparo was the subject of an 
earlier communication (see above, case no TJK 3/2012). 
