</p>
<p>The communication refers to the recent electoral process and outcome in the 
United States of America and emphasizes that this is an opportune moment in 
the US to advance equality and women&#8216;s human rights, including in political 
</p>
<p>and public life.  It also encourages the Government to fulfill its long-standing 
expression of intent to ratify the Convention on the Elimination of All Forms 
of Discrimination against Women.  
</p>
<p> 
 
 
 
