Association of Journalists (BAJ), and Messrs. Valiantsin Stefanovich, Aleh Hulak,  
member of the Belarusian Helsinki Committee (BHC), Andrey Dynko, editor-in-
chief of the independent newspaper &#8213;Nasha Niva&#8214;, and Harry Pahanyayla, 
